text: Vinessa Elizabeth Shaw (born 19 July 1976) is an American actress and model. Shaw was born in Los Angeles, California. She has starred in many movies since the early 1990s. These include Hocus Pocus, Ladybugs, the 2006 remake of The Hills Have Eyes, and Two Lovers. ==References== Category:Models from Los Angeles Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:1976 births Category:Living people
